Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在某天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.22,0:02:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长长的电话过后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:06.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她在我身旁哭了很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想错的并不是她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一直注视着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她总是比任何人都更体贴 比任何人都漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都更充实地活得
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听得到她的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:30.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁…谁…
